(October 26, 1962)

In decisions Nos. 1-4: Present — Bergan, P. J., Coon, Gibson, Reynolds and Taylor, JJ.

In the Matter of Arthur C. Ford et al., Appellants, v. Consolidated Cannonsville Highway & Utility Section et al., Respondents.

Appeal dismissed, without costs, unless appellant shall file and serve record, brief and note of issue for the January 1963 Term on or before December 1, 1962, in which event motion denied.
